#   technician     – person / team responsible
#   description    – what was performed
#   findings       – what was found
#   partsReplaced  – list of parts (may be empty)
#   durationHours  – duration of the work in hours
#   result         – COMPLETED | COMPLETED_WITH_FINDINGS | DEFERRED
#   hoursAtService – turbine operating hours at time of service

